original_title: These Are Not The Words Of One Who Is Oppressed By A Demon
overview: The Increasing Melodic Hiss Of Inner Mechanic Malfunction Signifies The Monstrous Destruction Of What Was Presented As “Reality.” Upon Collapse And In Lieu Of Charred Flesh, The Result Of A Methodical Withdrawal Of The Hearts Bloody Essence.
title: These Are Not The Words Of One Who Is Oppressed By A Demon
